Screen Open 0,256,256,4,0
Curs Off : Cls 2 : Hide On 
'Follow A,X,Y,D
X=128 : Y=128 : D=0
Dim M(3,1) : M(0,1)=-1 : M(1,0)=1 : M(2,1)=1 : M(3,0)=-1
Do 
   'ant moves 
   Add X,M(D,0) : Add Y,M(D,1)
   X=X and 255 : Y=Y and 255
   'square flips
   C=Point(X,Y)+1 : If C=3 Then C=0
   Plot X,Y,C
   'ant turns 
   If C=2 Then Inc D Else If C=0 Then Dec D
   D=D and 3
Loop 
